ygData.messageBody:
Oi, you two want to join my "Get rich quick organisation" ? 3 of us camp at
the 3 brew barrels in Freeport(North, West and East freeport have brew
barrels) and keep making wine. Can generate around 30+ plat per hour.

So far, pottery stinks. The merchants who sell firing sheets are always
missing (the goon at e-commons and the other one in Misty thinkets.) Feel
like vomiting blood
